Region: Sub-national gas sales and numbers of customers, 2013

Local Authority: (1) Customers with an annual consumption of 73,200 kWh or lower which will include some small industrial and commercial consumers.
(2) These local authorities have no connection to mainline gas pipelines.
(3) This area contains at least one major power station or large industrial consumer whose consumption has not been included in the data.
